reviews.review_text: gotta love it toataly smoking all said that needed to b said

The best Throwing Stones of all time! Crunch crunch crunch. Keep On Growing. This show definitely captures the magic that came out of the boys at Alpine. One of the best things about this show is that the better your stereo equipment is, the more you will get out of it. The sound after Jerry kicks in toward the end of Keep On Growing is as good as it gets.
crackling with energy the combination of the band's performance as well as the quality of this aud makes this a five-star listen... a high energy show from start to finish
